<h3 id="latency-issues" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#latency-issues" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Latency Issues</h3>
<p>Latency is a key consideration for accessing data in any kind of storage. Regional, zone, and CDN considerations must be made.</p>
